<p class="noindent"> Department Website: <a href="https://cam.uchicago.edu/academics/undergraduate-programs/" target="_blank">https://cam.uchicago.edu/academics/undergraduate-programs/</a></p><a name="programofstudy"></a>
<h3>Program of Study</h3>




<p>The Departments of<span> Computer Science, Mathematics, and Statistics offer a BS in Computational and Applied Mathematics. The program is designed for students who intend to specialize in computational and/or applied mathematics, as well as students who want to acquire a strong quantitative background to be applied in such varied areas as physics, biological sciences, engineering, operations research, economics, and finance.</span></p>




<a name="summaryofrequirements"></a>
